						               													<description>The life of the little stuffed Teddy comes to life at night, his duty is to take care of the dreams of his child, throughout the hours of the night he must go through a series of adventures with the aim that his child wakes up as calm possible, but you must be careful, the world of nightmares is open and Little Guss is prowling the room, you will have to collect as many magic buttons as possible to help protect your child's dreams.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The Teddy's Adventures is a roll &amp;amp; write style game but with buttons instead of dice, it is played by taking colored buttons out of a bag, from these buttons the active player will choose which buttons will be painted in each section of his game sheet and which button It will be eliminated, in addition to which button the other players will paint, the game sheet will fill with colors as the rules explain, and you will have to check the progress of the board of the world of nightmares that can trigger the end sooner than provided. Once the end of the game is triggered, points will be counted in each section of the sheet and the player who scores more points than the others will win.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the designer&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
